<p style="Normal" xid="449" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">  (Rubyschool lesson 48)</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="450" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="451" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Scaffolding</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="452" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Создадим новое приложение в </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Rails</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> и назовем его </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">toy_app</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">. Чтобы создать новое приложение мы как обычно пишем в консоли </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">rails new toy_app</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="453" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">В проекте у нас будет две таблицы, одна </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">users</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> c полями </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">id-integer; name - string и email- string, </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">вторая </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">microposts </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">c полями  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">id - integer; content-text; user_id integer. </c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="454" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Создадим первую таблицу при помощи скафолдинга. Откроем консоль и напишем </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="456" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">rails g scaffold User name:string email:string . </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Эта команда создает одновременно модель, одновременно контроллер, одновременно представления, одновременно тесты итд. Эта команда создаст все что нам нужно для сущности юзер. Также эта команда прописывает маршрут. Добавим миграцию нашей модели </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">bundle exec rake db:migrate</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="459" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Тепер запустим сервер и посмотрим что у нас появилось в браузере. В браузере видим что все заработало, можно создавать новых пользователей редактировать их и удалять.</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="461" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Единственное что нам немешало бы изменить то это начальную страницу. Допишем в файле config/routes.rb строчку </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">root ‘users#index’</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">. Теперь приложение будет показывать начальную страницу со всеми нашеми пользователями . Какие есть недостатки при создании таблиц через скаффолдинг или что нужно дописывать ручками.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="462" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">1) Нет валидации</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="463" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">2)Нет авторизации, любой пользователь может править нашу страницу без нашего ведома.</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="464" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">3)Нет тестов. Тесты есть но они прокрывает только основные действия, тесты тоже надо будет писать ручками.</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="465" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">4) Нет нормального оформления страницы которое тожже предстоит допиливать.</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="466" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="467" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Теперь создадим сущность </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Micropst</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">. Зайдем опять в консоль и при помощи скафолдинга создадим новую таблицу командой </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">rails g scaffold Micropost content:text user_id:integer</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">.  Теперь добавим валидацию в модель </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">micropost</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="471" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="468" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none">class Micropost &lt; ApplicationRecord<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="469" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in">  validates :content, length: {maximum: 140}<c></c></p>
